[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m897[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mWINPR_ASSERT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpExpectedBlockType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m898[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m899[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pExpectedBlockType != WBT_EXTENSION[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m900[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m901[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mWLog_Print[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext->priv->log, WLOG_ERROR, [0m[32m"message unexpected [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mwants a tileset"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m902[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn FALSE;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m903[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m904[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m905[0m[39m:    [0m[39m*pExpectedBlockType = WBT_FRAME_END;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m906[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlibfreerdp/codec/rfx.[0m[1;92mc:687[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m707[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m687[0m[39m:static INLINE BOOL [0m[1;35mrfx_process_message_frame_end[0m[1;39m([0m[39mRFX_CONTEXT* WINPR_RESTRICT [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontext,[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m688[0m[39m:                                                 RFX_MESSAGE* WINPR_RESTRICT [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmessage,[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m689[0m[39m:                                                 wStream* WINPR_RESTRICT s,[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m690[0m[39m:                                                 UINT16* WINPR_RESTRICT [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpExpectedBlockType[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m691[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m692[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mWINPR_ASSERT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m693[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mWINPR_ASSERT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext->priv[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m694[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mWINPR_ASSERT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mmessage[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m695[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mWINPR_ASSERT[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m696[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mWINPR_ASSERT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpExpectedBlockType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m697[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m698[0m[39m:    [0m[39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m*pExpectedBlockType != WBT_FRAME_END[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m699[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m700[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mWLog_Print[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext->priv->log, WLOG_ERROR, [0m[32m"message unexpected, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mwants WBT_FRAME_END"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m701[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn FALSE;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m702[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m703[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m704[0m[39m:    [0m[39m*pExpectedBlockType = WBT_FRAME_BEGIN;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m705[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mWLog_Print[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext->priv->log, WLOG_DEBUG, [0m[32m"RFX_FRAME_END"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m706[0m[39m:    [0m[39mreturn TRUE;[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m707[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBased on the evaluation report and code analysis, I've identified the root cause of[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe persistent crash:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### The Problem[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe previous patch only removed **lines [0m[1;36m674[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m680[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe code that reads and modifies[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe global variables[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, but left these critical components intact:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Global variables** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m142[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m143[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m179[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m180[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: `metadataBlock` and [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`metadataData` remain declared[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **The crash location** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m734[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: `*[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mmetadataBlock = metadataData;` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstill executes[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **The malicious handler** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m709[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m736[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: `rfx_process_message_metadata` [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunction still exists[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **The handler invocation** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m1319[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1322[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: WBT_METADATA case still calls the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhandler[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWhen the fuzzer sends a WBT_METADATA block, the malicious handler still executes [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand attempts to write to `metadataBlock`, which now retains its initial value [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m&explicit_bzero` [0m[1;39m([0m[39ma function pointer address[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. Since the code at lines [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m674[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m680[0m[39m that modifies this address was removed, the write happens at a slightly [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdifferent but still invalid address, causing the same segmentation fault.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Evidence This is Malicious Code[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Not in legitimate protocol**: WBT_METADATA [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0xCCC8[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is never written by [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mencoding functions[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **No test data contains it**: Legitimate test samples don't include WBT_METADATA[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mblocks[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Bypasses validation**: WBT_METADATA is outside the range check `[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mWBT_CONTEXT, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWBT_EXTENSION[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`, avoiding codecId/channelId validation[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Global variables are suspicious**: Using globals initialized to function [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpointer addresses for metadata is highly unusual[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Arbitrary memory write**: The code computes an arbitrary address and writes to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit based on untrusted input[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **No legitimate usage**: No legitimate code initializes, uses, or depends on [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthese components[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mRemove **all five components** of the malicious backdoor code:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Remove Global Variable Declarations [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLines [0m[1;36m142[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m143[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m179[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m180[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDelete:[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```c[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUINT64 metadataBlock = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m&explicit_bzero;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDelete:[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```c[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mUINT64 metadataData = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: These global variables are never used by legitimate code. They exist[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msolely to support the malicious write operation.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Remove Malicious Data Reading in `rfx_process_message_frame_begin` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLines [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m674[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m680[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDelete the conditional block:[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```c[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mStream_GetRemainingLength[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= [0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        UINT64 blockOffset = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mStream_Read_UINT64[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms, blockOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mStream_Read_UINT64[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms, metadataData[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        metadataBlock += blockOffset;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The legitimate `rfx_write_message_frame_begin` only writes [0m[1;36m14[0m[39m bytes total[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This extra read of [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m bytes [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[39m × UINT64[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is not part of the RemoteFX [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mspecification[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- It allows arbitrary address computation based on fuzzer input[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This was removed in the previous patch, and should remain removed[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Remove Entire `rfx_process_message_metadata` Function [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLines [0m[1;36m709[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m736[0m[1;39m)[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDelete the entire function from lines [0m[1;36m709[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m736[0m[39m.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This function is never called by legitimate code paths[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- It executes the malicious write: `*[0m[1;39m([0m[39mUINT64*[0m[1;39m)[0m[39mmetadataBlock = metadataData;`[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No legitimate protocol flow requires this function[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The state machine doesn't include WBT_METADATA in valid transitions[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Remove WBT_METADATA Case from Switch Statement [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLines [0m[1;36m1319[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1322[0m[1;39m)[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIn the `rfx_process_message` function's switch statement, delete:[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```c[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcase WBT_METADATA:[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    ok = [0m[1;35mrfx_process_message_metadata[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext, message, subStream,[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                     &context->expectedDataBlockType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    break;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This case invokes the malicious handler[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- WBT_METADATA blocks should be treated as invalid/unknown block types[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After removal, WBT_METADATA will fall through to the `default` case and be [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrejected with [0m[32m"unknown blockType"[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. Optional: Remove WBT_METADATA Constant Definition[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIn `libfreerdp/codec/rfx_constants.h`, optionally remove:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```c[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m#define WBT_METADATA [0m[1;36m0xCCC8[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: While not strictly necessary [0m[1;39m([0m[39mkeeping it won't cause harm[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, removing[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit completely eliminates all traces of the malicious code.[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Preserved Functionality[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAll legitimate RemoteFX protocol functionality remains intact:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Header Message Handlers [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUnchanged[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `rfx_process_message_sync` - validates magic number and version[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `rfx_process_message_codec_versions` - validates codec parameters[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `rfx_process_message_channels` - validates channel configuration[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `rfx_process_message_context` - validates context settings[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Data Message Handlers [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUnchanged[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `rfx_process_message_frame_begin` - after removal of lines [0m[1;36m674[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m680[0m[39m, properly [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreads only frameIdx [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m4[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and numRegions [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m2[0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `rfx_process_message_region` - processes rectangle regions[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `rfx_process_message_tileset` - processes compressed tile data[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `rfx_process_message_frame_end` - marks frame completion[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### State Machine [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUnchanged[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe legitimate state transitions continue to work:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `WBT_FRAME_BEGIN` → `WBT_REGION` → `WBT_EXTENSION` → `WBT_FRAME_END` → [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrepeat[0m[1;39m)[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Encoding Functions [0m[1;39m([0m[39mUnchanged[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAll encoding functions [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`rfx_write_message_*`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remain unchanged and never write [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWBT_METADATA blocks.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Why This Fix Works[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Removes the crash location**: Line [0m[1;36m734[0m[39m's wild write is eliminated[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Removes the trigger**: WBT_METADATA blocks now fall through to the default [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcase and are rejected[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Removes the attack surface**: No code path can exploit the removed components[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Preserves legitimate functionality**: All standard RemoteFX protocol [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperations continue to work[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Follows defense in depth**: Removes all related malicious components, not just[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe symptom[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Potential Side Effects[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**[0m[3;35mNone[0m[39m expected** because:[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No legitimate code references these components[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- No legitimate test cases contain WBT_METADATA blocks[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The encoding side never generates WBT_METADATA blocks[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The removed code is isolated and self-contained[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All legitimate message handlers remain functional[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Similar Patterns in Codebase[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe legitimate handlers all follow this pattern:[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Validate stream length[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Read data into context or message structures[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Validate read values[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Update state machine via `pExpectedBlockType`[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Never use global variables for protocol state[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Never perform arbitrary memory writes[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe removed malicious code violated all these patterns.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch removes lines [0m[1;36m674[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m682[0m[39m from `libfreerdp/codec/rfx.c`:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```c[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mStream_Read_UINT64[0m[1;39m([0m[39ms, metadataData[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        metadataBlock += blockOffset;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis conditional block reads metadata information from a stream if at least [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m bytes[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mare available. The removal appears to be an attempt to prevent reading potentially [0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis exactly [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m lines earlier, matching the number of lines removed in the patch. This[0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m731[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[1;35mWLog_Print[0m[1;39m([0m[39mcontext->priv->log, WLOG_ERROR, [0m[32m"invalid magic number [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m0x%08"[0m[39m PRIX32 [0m[32m""[0m[39m, magic[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m732[0m[39m:    [0m[39m        [0m[39mreturn FALSE;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
